Rating: 2
Good with a lot of modifications. Doubled the cumin; added 2 tsp curry powder; a pinch of cayenne pepper; dash of nutmeg; 6-8 cloves of garlic; 1/2 C diced red onion; one diced shallot; 1 tsp fresh ginger, diced. Sauteed the garlic, shallots, and onion in the pot before starting, then added all other ingredients. With all of these modifications it had some kick, otherwise would be very bland. With modifications would give it 3 forks.

